    drm/omap: use drm_atomic_helper_shutdown()
    
    Use drm_atomic_helper_shutdown() to ensure that all crtcs are disabled
    when unloading the driver.
    
    Signed-off-by: Tomi Valkeinen <tomi.valkeinen@ti.com>

